  "introHtml": "I’m a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>software developer</span> and enjoy <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>building useful tools</span> that <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>solve real problems</span>. I’ve worked with <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>cloud infrastructure</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>REST APIs</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>automation</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>front-end performance</span>, and various other <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>stacks</span> which I've shared below. I find myself drawn to the process of <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>taking</span> an <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>intricate problem</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>breaking</span> it into <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>smaller pieces</span>, and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>turning</span> it into a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>solution</span> to <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>benefit users</span>. <br><br> Outside of work, I’m a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>proud father</span>, an <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>avid gamer</span>, and a <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>longtime PC enthusiast</span>. I’ve <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>built</span> several <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>desktops</span> from <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>scratch</span>, including the ones I <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>game on</span>, with <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>favorites</span> like <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Kerbal Space Program</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Factorio</span>, and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>Portal 1+2</span>. I also enjoy <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>skiing</span>, <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>longboarding</span>, and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>building</span> and <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>flying</span> my own <span class='text-maintext font-bold'>remote-controlled airplanes</span>.",
